
MeshBerry - include directory
=============================

This directory is intended for project header files.

Use for global headers that should be accessible from any source file.

Example structure:

|--include
|  |--version.h         (version constants)
|  |--features.h        (feature flags)
|  |--README (this file)

Most headers should live in src/ alongside their implementations:
- src/config.h          (pin definitions and constants)
- src/drivers/*.h       (hardware driver interfaces)
- src/mesh/*.h          (mesh protocol headers)
- src/ui/*.h            (user interface headers)

More information:
https://docs.platformio.org/page/projectconf/section_env_build.html
